==Critical reception==
As of 27 October 2009, [[CNET]] reported a total of 1,074,578 downloads for K-Lite Mega Codec Pack 5.2 since it was released on 12 October 2009. User ratings gave it an average of 4.5 out of 5 stars, but it was only reviewed by 87 people.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://download.cnet.com/K-Lite-Mega-Codec-Pack/3000-13632_4-10794603.html |title=K-Lite Mega Codec Pack 5.2 |publisher=[[CNET]] |date=12 October 2009 |accessdate=27 October 2009}}</ref> Meanwhile, CNET reported only 122,552 downloads for K-Lite Codec Pack Full Edition 5.2 (released on the same date), however it also received an average user rating of 4.5 out of 5 stars, albeit from only seven reviewers.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://download.cnet.com/K-Lite-Codec-Pack-Full/3000-2170_4-64246.html |title=K-Lite Codec Pack Full 5.2 |publisher=[[CNET]] |date=12 October 2009 |accessdate=27 October 2009}}</ref> No CNET editors had reviewed these products up until this time.

On the same date, Betanews FileForums reported a rating of 4.7 out of 5 based on 2,346 votes for K-Lite Mega Codec Pack 5.2.0, and 9,416,511 downloads.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://fileforum.betanews.com/detail/KLite-Mega-Codec-Pack/1080441198/1 |title=K-Lite Mega Codec Pack â Free Download and Reviews |publisher=fileforum.betanews.com |date=13 October 2009 |accessdate=27 October 2009}}</ref> FileForum did not have an entry for K-Lite Codec Pack 5.2 Full.

[[Softpedia]] reported K-Lite Mega Codec Pack 5.2 and K-Lite Codec Pack 5.2 Update to have been downloaded a combined total of 2,011,113 times after their release on 12 October 2009, and gave them a user rating of 4.4 out of 5 based on 2,281 votes. K-Lite Mega Codec Pack was chosen as a Softpedia Pick.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.softpedia.com/get/Multimedia/Video/Codec-Packs-Video-Codecs/KLite-Mega-Codec-Pack.shtml |title=K-Lite Mega Codec Pack â Softpedia |publisher=[[Softpedia]] |date=13 October 2009 |accessdate=27 October 2009}}</ref> Softpedia also reported K-Lite Codec Pack 5.2 Full, K-Lite Codec Pack Full 5.2 Update, and K-Lite Codec Pack 2.7 64-bit Edition to have been downloaded a combined total of 1,452,750 times up until this date, and to have received a user rating of 4.3 out of 5 from 2,082 users. K-Lite Codec Pack Full 5.2 was also a Softpedia Pick.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.softpedia.com/get/Multimedia/Video/Codec-Packs-Video-Codecs/KLite-Codec-Pack.shtml |title=K-Lite Codec Pack Full Update 5.2.0 Build 20091013 / 5.2.0 / 2.7.0 - x64 |publisher=Softpedia |date=13 October 2009 |accessdate=27 October 2009}}</ref>

[[SnapFiles]] also highly praised K-Lite Codec Pack Full edition, giving it five stars.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.snapfiles.com/get/k-lite-full.html|title=K-Lite Codec Pack (Full) Freeware download and review - installs popular audio and video codecs from SnapFiles|publisher=SnapFiles|date=29 October 2009|accessdate=14 November 2009}}</ref>

